.</p>
            <p>This is a Countdown solver. With this tool you can enter inp=
uts from Countdown
            <!--
            <a href=3D"http://www.channel4.com/programmes/countdown">Countd=
own</a>
            -->
            letters and numbers games and have solutions calculated.</p>
            <p>No promises are made about the completeness of the dictionar=
y for the letters game solver, though the numbers game solver is able to so=
lve any solvable game. The letters game solver is also useful for solving t=
he Countdown Conundrum and the Teatime Teaser.</p>
